      (altRightBasis.tensorProduct altRightBasis) (altRightBasis.tensorProduct altRightBasis)
      (TensorProduct.map (altRightHanded.ρ M) (altRightHanded.ρ M)))
      *ᵥ ((Finsupp.linearEquivFunOnFinite ℂ ℂ (Fin 2 × Fin 2))
